    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Doxypypy Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Doxypypy</application> package is a doxygen filter for
python.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&doxypypy-download-http;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&doxypypy-download-ftp;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Soma de verificao MD5: &doxypypy-md5sum;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tamanho da transferncia: &doxypypy-size;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Espao em disco estimado exigido: &doxypypy-buildsize;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tempo de construo estimado: &doxypypy-time;
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Dependncias de Doxypypy</bridgehead>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect5">Exigida</bridgehead>
      <para role="required">
        <xref linkend="chardet"/> and <xref role="runtime" linkend="doxygen"/> (at
run time)
      </para>

    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Doxypypy</title>

    <para> Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user doxypypy</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste funcional.
    </para>

    </sect3>

